🇳🇿 In New Zealand, no one is exempt from the strict #coronavirus prevention measures -- not even PM Jacinda Ardern.

The PM, her fiance and a group of friends were turned away from a cafe in Wellington because it had already reached its customer limit https://t.co/sAWy0c6o7t https://t.co/A77wOp5Ms8
